Title: Luxury Zero Gravity Massage Chair
Body HTML:
Description

The Luxury Zero Gravity Massage Chair is equipped with the latest “Smart Chair” technology. The “Smart Chair” is a computer body scan technology which maps out the size, shape, curvature of your back and adjusts the rollers to each individual user. With five massage techniques, this chair offers the ultimate in relaxation.

Maximum Relaxation

The “SL” back rail is engineered to match the curvature of the human back, Maximum Relax, allowing for maximum massage touch points of the mechanical rollers. Additionally, the biomechanical rollers have been engineered to mimic the massage techniques and feel of the human hand. Other features include five massage techniques, 6 pre-programmed massage modes and carbon fiber heat for a comfortable heat therapy massage to loosen up sore stiff muscles.

Full-Body Therapy

The Luxury Zero Gravity Massage Chair not only provides an unprecedented back massage, it's also a complete full-body massage chair equipped with 28 total airbags along with a massive air pump which provides a compression massage for your feet, legs, arms, shoulders and hips. Take the next step and invest in promoting the healthier active lifestyle you desire with massage therapy from the Luxury Zero Gravity Massage Chair. Sit back and relax with the most soothing experience ever!

 

Assembled Size

58.4" x 30.1" x 33.8"

Title: Ultra Intelligent Design Zero Gravity Massage Chair
Body HTML:
Description

The Ultra Intelligent Design Zero Gravity Massage Chair (Assorted Colors) is a smart chair designed to give your body a targeted massage to aid with muscle soreness and general aches and pains. If you are looking for the best zero gravity massage chair on the market, you should consider investing in this Ultra Intelligent Design Zero Gravity Massage Chair.

What Is a Smart Chair?

The "smart chair" is a chair utilizing a computer body scan technology to individualize your massage experience by mapping out your shape, size and the curvature of your back. Based on this data, the chair will adjust its rollers to give you a targeted massage.

What Features Does the Ultra Intelligent Design Zero Gravity Massage Chair Offer?

This advanced zero gravity massage chair features an "SL" back rail created to mimic the curvature of your spine. This allows the mechanical rollers to adjust and facilitate a massage with maximum touch points along your back. Each biomechanical roller is intended to simulate the massage techniques and feel of the human hand.

Additional features for this massage chair include five massage techniques, five pre-programmed massage modes and heated back rollers to facilitate a true spa experience. The control panel for the chair is located on the armrest and includes a USB port. The back rollers operate under three separate speed settings and three different intensity settings, giving you options for your full body massage. This zero gravity massage chair also comes with 28 total airbags and a large air pump to provide you with a compression massage for your lower extremities, shoulders and hips.

For more technological features, this massage chair comes with "zero gravity" mode up to 118 degrees. Additionally, it has Bluetooth CD speakers so you can create the ambiance of your choice.

This year, take the step to invest in your health and have consistent, convenient access to professional massage therapy with the Ultra Intelligent Design Zero Gravity Massage Chair.

Policies & plans

Specifications

  • Smart chair computer body scan technology
  • 5 massage techniques
  • 28 airbags
  • 5 preprogrammed massage modes
  • SL 53" long shape Back Rail
  • Zero wall design to within 2" from wall
  • Heated back rollers
  • 3 speed settings
  • 3 intensity settings
  • Control panel in armrest with USB
  • Zero gravity mode to 118 degrees
  • Bluetooth 3D speakers
  • Leg extension of 5.9" for users between 5'0" to 6'3"
  • Mechanical rollers for feet and heals
  • LED Rremote
  • Weight capacity 260 lbs.
  • Auto reset mode when turned off
